How to enforce the best practices within a team?

    How to ensure best practices within projects
	
	Linter:
		Eslint - " A pluggable and configurable linter tool for identifying and reporting on patterns in JavaScript." 
                    (https://eslint.org/docs/rules/)

    Code Analysers paid solutions:
        SonarQube
        Codacy

    Functionality used with Git, Linters & Code Analysers

        Validate if there are no erros in the code respository, if there are, prevent the deploy of the code.
        Notify the programmer via email if the code commit to repository has some sort of error
        Manage rules and legacy code by management